{
  "stem": "11184.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they said-- they put out signs that they have already so many people that they couldn't have anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me and my mother and a few others had-- still had to sleep in the-- in the train, which was-- I felt-- I felt it so unfair, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was not an aggressive, neither was mother, to just go in and say, hey, you just let me stay in a warm-- in a warm room, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't do that, and they didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Americans didn't?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Americans didn't, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said that, well, it's already occupied, already occupied.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that made me a little angry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they-- they fed us, you know, with the bread, the-- the white bread, what we weren't accustomed to.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we waited a couple days, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was always on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was never-- I was never in a-- but they said the next day they're gonna take us to a camp, to a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was over.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was a very sad feeling in my heart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where am I going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where are we going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the recollection of the family, the recollection of the family, you know--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All that-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very, very kind of-- with-- with the happiness, there was sadness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where are we now?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For once you had a minute to catch your breath and see what's you'd lost.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, you know, life went on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came to the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Feldafing, where I-- we met General Eisenhower there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh my God.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
